==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Tagal
<hw>Ta*gal"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>One of a
Malayan race, mainly of central Luzon, next to the Visayans the most
numerous of the native peoples of the Philippines. Nearly all are
Christians and many are highly educated.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>The language of the Tagals; Tagalog.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Tagalog</ent>⟦br⟧
